37 directories, 19 files

Before using do this step

Step 1: create project, prepare files needed. 
Copy the nonfree folder from opencv2.4.5\modules\nonfree\include\opencv2\ to OpenCV-2.4.5-android-sdk\sdk\native\jni\include\opencv2\. What we actually need are nonfree.hpp and features2d.hpp. But it's OK if you also copy other files.

IF you have problems with OpenCV after "installation", then you might want to install ia32-libs.
